name: CellBerry速
description: CellBerry速 is a high-quality Aronia, chokeberry extract from the Aronia melanocarpa plant, found in eastern North America. CellBerry速 is patented for the purpose of promoting weight loss. It undergoes a proprietary extraction process and is standardized to anthocyanin content. These dark black chokeberries have a deep purple, an almost black pigment that is from the rich, dark phenolic anthocyanins. These powerful compounds in CellBerry速 have been shown in clinical research to have a wide range of health-enhancing benefits.
